---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("November 23 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

// FAQ Schema data for AEO optimization
const faqSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  mainEntity: []
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Black Friday Special: The Gift of a Clean Home | The Valley Clean Team"
  description="Give the ultimate gift this holiday season: a clean home! Discover our exclusive Black Friday specials on professional cleaning services across AL and TN."
  ogImage="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/iKQIBhpKVL2XVPgU7HMd/media/6920802945dc047d65b4ec5d.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="Black Friday Special: The Gift of a Clean Home"
    description="Give the ultimate gift this holiday season: a clean home! Discover our exclusive Black Friday specials on professional cleaning services across AL and TN."
    publishDate="November 23 2026"
    author={author}
  />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Promo/Conversion
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Black Friday Special: The Gift of a Clean Home
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming November 23 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>November 23 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>Why Choose a Black Friday Cleaning Special in The Shoals?</h2>
<p><strong>Unlock the ultimate gift of time and serenity with The Valley Clean Team's Black Friday Special. Secure a pristine, stress-free home in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas with our expertly tailored cleaning services, starting at an unbeatable price.</strong></p>
<p>This Black Friday, we offer more than just a clean home—we deliver the gift of time and tranquility. With our exclusive offer, you can enjoy a spotless space and reclaim your weekends, all while experiencing the precision and reliability that only a veteran-owned service can provide.</p>

<h3>The Advantage of a Professional Clean</h3>
<p>Imagine coming home to a sanctuary where every surface gleams, and every room feels fresh. Our trained cleaning specialists employ systematic approaches to restore and maintain your home’s pristine condition.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Precision:</strong> We follow military-grade checklists to ensure every detail is addressed.</li>
  <li><strong>Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs):</strong> Every task is executed with accountability and integrity.</li>
  <li><strong>Guaranteed Satisfaction:</strong> We stand by our promise for a perfect clean, every time.</li>
</ul>
<p>Investing in a professional clean means more than just tidiness. It’s about enhancing your living space, improving your quality of life, and ensuring a healthy environment for you and your loved ones.</p>

<h3>What Makes Our Black Friday Special Unique?</h3>
<p>The Valley Clean Team is committed to offering a transparent and straightforward service that sets us apart. Here’s exactly what you can expect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Exclusive Pricing:</strong> Take advantage of our Black Friday rates starting at just $125.</li>
  <li><strong>Tailored Services:</strong> Each cleaning package is customized to meet your specific needs and preferences.</li>
  <li><strong>Community Focused:</strong> As a local business, we are dedicated to serving The Shoals & Surrounding Areas with respect and accountability.</li>
</ul>
<p>This offer is designed to give you the ultimate peace of mind and a home you'll be proud to show off over the holidays.</p>

<h3>How to Secure Your Black Friday Cleaning Deal</h3>
<p>The process is simple and transparent—here’s how it works:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Visit our website and select the ‘Black Friday Special’ option.</li>
  <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Choose your preferred cleaning package and schedule.</li>
  <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Book your service and enjoy the peace of mind that comes with a guaranteed clean.</li>
</ul>
<p>Our straightforward booking process ensures that you’re never left guessing about costs or services. We pride ourselves on clear communication and upfront pricing.</p>

<h3>Why The Valley Clean Team?</h3>
<p>We are not just another cleaning service. As a veteran and women-owned business, we bring a level of discipline and dedication that is unmatched. Our team is meticulously trained, vetted, and committed to delivering results that exceed expectations.</p>
<p>Choosing The Valley Clean Team means choosing a partner in maintaining the highest standards for your home. Our local roots in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas reinforce our dedication to community-focused service and support.</p>

<h3>Reclaim Your Time—Book Your Guaranteed Clean Today</h3>
<p>This Black Friday, give yourself the gift of a spotless home and the freedom to enjoy it. Our exclusive offer won't last long, so act now. <strong>Book online today and secure your tailored cleaning service with The Valley Clean Team.</strong></p>
<p>Elevate your living space with precision and care that only our veteran-owned team can provide. Experience the difference and enjoy a home that meets the highest standards of cleanliness and comfort.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">November 23 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
